'''宾夕法尼亚州同性婚姻'''于2014年5月20日合法化。20日[[美国宾夕法尼亚中区联邦地区法院|美国联邦地区法院]]法官裁定1996年州禁止[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]的法律是违宪的。<ref>{{cite news|last=Botelho|first=Greg|title=Federal judge rules same-sex marriage ban in Pennsylvania is unconstitutional|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/05/20/us/pennsylvania-same-sex-marriage/|accessdate=2014-05-21|newspaper=CNN|date=2014-05-20|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120005346/https://edition.cnn.com/2014/05/20/us/pennsylvania-same-sex-marriage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

宾夕法尼亚州此前不承认[[民事结合|民事结合]]，是美国东北部地区最后一个同性伴侣不能合法结合的州。<ref>{{cite news|last=Heller|first=Karen|title=Pennsylvania stands alone on yet another issue|url=http://articles.philly.com/2013-10-24/news/43327516_1_medicaid-expansion-state-song-gay-rights|accessdate=2013-12-03|newspaper=Philly.com|date=2013-10-24|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072634/http://articles.philly.com/2013-10-24/news/43327516_1_medicaid-expansion-state-song-gay-rights|dead-url=no}}</ref>

